WEBVTT

00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:17.220
[Longwan Village, Hanzhou, 2010]
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:25.480
Why are you drinking so much?

00:00:25.480 --> 00:00:27.140
Aren't you driving tomorrow?

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:30.370
I don't need you worrying about me.

00:00:33.910 --> 00:00:34.070
[Ding Tiejun, Longwan Villager]

00:00:34.070 --> 00:00:35.470
And if I don't worry about you, who will?

00:00:35.470 --> 00:00:36.400
I'm your father.

00:00:41.240 --> 00:00:41.900
Xiaoshuai.

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.390
Just because you're earning money now,

00:00:45.390 --> 00:00:46.600
don't think you’ve grown wings

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:48.130
and I've got no say anymore.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.400
Don't think I don't know.

00:00:50.710 --> 00:00:52.040
All you ever think about

00:00:52.350 --> 00:00:53.350
is hanging around

00:00:53.430 --> 00:00:55.070
with those shady people from Longwan.

00:00:55.070 --> 00:00:55.670
Am I wrong?

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.840
How can you ever
amount to anything like that?

00:00:57.840 --> 00:00:59.370
I can't amount to anything.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:00.960
Can you?

00:01:03.790 --> 00:01:05.230
I just don't get it.

00:01:06.350 --> 00:01:08.350
We're all from Longwan,

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:09.789
they've built such big businesses,

00:01:09.789 --> 00:01:12.000
and it's got nothing to do
with you—not a single cent.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.080
What's the point
of having a big business anyway?

00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:16.480
Don't you remember how Wen Jiangyong died?

00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:18.400
Always fighting and showing off,

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:19.350
competing for everything,

00:01:19.350 --> 00:01:20.880
he ended up losing his life.

00:01:21.350 --> 00:01:22.920
When he's dead, it's over for him.

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:24.400
But what about his family left behind?

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:25.330
What about them?

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:28.039
Well, why do you need to worry about them?

00:01:28.510 --> 00:01:30.350
At least he fought for something.

00:01:30.350 --> 00:01:31.410
He was not like you.

00:01:31.710 --> 00:01:33.910
You've been a pushover your whole life.

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:38.000
I don't think I'm a pushover.

00:01:38.350 --> 00:01:39.509
I live my own life

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:42.009
and being honest is better than anything!

00:01:47.120 --> 00:01:50.120
Our family is destined
to be looked down upon forever.

00:03:07.700 --> 00:03:17.900
[The Punishment]

00:03:18.060 --> 00:03:18.300
[Punish those who commit crimes
and make mistakes]

00:03:18.300 --> 00:03:18.540
[so as to discipline them,]

00:03:18.540 --> 00:03:19.030
[and execute those
who violate the prohibitions]

00:03:19.030 --> 00:03:20.000
[so as to terrify would-be violators.]

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.950
[Guanzi – On Laws and Standards]

00:03:22.590 --> 00:03:25.340
[Episode 28]

00:03:27.710 --> 00:03:28.430
Tianye.

00:03:29.150 --> 00:03:30.680
What are you really

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:33.160
thinking about you and Ziyi?

00:03:37.910 --> 00:03:38.710
Nothing much.

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:42.560
I've made up my mind.

00:03:45.079 --> 00:03:46.079
Made up your mind?

00:03:46.590 --> 00:03:47.720
What does that mean?

00:03:53.310 --> 00:03:54.440
Divorce, of course.

00:03:59.280 --> 00:03:59.990
Divorce?

00:04:02.470 --> 00:04:03.200
Is that okay?

00:04:13.080 --> 00:04:14.540
Baoying is still so young.

00:04:15.590 --> 00:04:16.720
Is that really okay?

00:04:20.079 --> 00:04:22.340
I've already signed the divorce papers.

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:23.720
I...

00:04:26.070 --> 00:04:27.930
I think they'd both be better off

00:04:28.310 --> 00:04:29.360
without me.

00:04:30.370 --> 00:04:31.370
What do you think?

00:04:34.909 --> 00:04:35.720
Maybe.

00:04:40.020 --> 00:04:40.940
Perhaps.

00:04:54.090 --> 00:04:55.460
What are you all doing?

00:05:02.030 --> 00:05:03.830
How about I sit alone for a while?

00:05:09.070 --> 00:05:09.600
Well.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:10.650
Peng.

00:05:10.690 --> 00:05:11.220
Tianfei.

00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:14.680
I'll show you around the back. Let's go.

00:05:14.920 --> 00:05:15.430
Okay.

00:05:25.510 --> 00:05:27.240
Since you've made up your mind,

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:28.740
you should quickly

00:05:28.870 --> 00:05:29.750
get it done.

00:06:11.430 --> 00:06:12.390
This is the car.

00:06:13.430 --> 00:06:15.830
The traffic police
captured this same vehicle.

00:06:15.830 --> 00:06:16.630
They said

00:06:17.800 --> 00:06:19.070
on the night He Gang disappeared

00:06:19.070 --> 00:06:20.720
this scrapped car was driven to the dock

00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:21.980
and never moved again.

00:06:59.070 --> 00:07:01.130
Could He Gang be on one of these ships?

00:07:02.170 --> 00:07:03.030
It's possible.

00:07:04.310 --> 00:07:06.040
He'd be too exposed on the dock.

00:07:06.830 --> 00:07:08.230
It's different on a ship.

00:07:09.510 --> 00:07:10.750
If he sails off to sea,

00:07:11.970 --> 00:07:14.240
it would be like
finding a needle in a haystack.

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:15.570
Look at all these ships.

00:07:15.750 --> 00:07:18.030
Coming and going every day,

00:07:18.630 --> 00:07:20.800
and some don't even
return to port the same day.

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:22.530
How are we supposed to find him?

00:07:22.830 --> 00:07:24.230
As Captain Qin would say.

00:07:25.270 --> 00:07:26.330
Just keep looking.

00:07:26.390 --> 00:07:28.660
Even if we can't find him,
we have to keep looking.

00:07:28.660 --> 00:07:29.190
Alright.

00:07:29.870 --> 00:07:31.600
Let's take our time searching.

00:07:44.540 --> 00:07:47.220
Get all the surveillance footage
from around here.

00:07:47.220 --> 00:07:47.700
Okay.

00:08:01.790 --> 00:08:02.440
Mr. Biao.

00:08:02.770 --> 00:08:03.910
The money from Longwan

00:08:03.910 --> 00:08:05.970
was indeed transferred to Qin Limin.

00:08:08.360 --> 00:08:09.190
Report it.

00:08:09.800 --> 00:08:10.530
Understood.

00:08:21.310 --> 00:08:23.040
Your brother is at Shekou Port.

00:08:23.280 --> 00:08:25.280
But we don't know which ship he's on.

00:08:25.310 --> 00:08:26.360
How do you get him out?

00:08:26.360 --> 00:08:27.960
That depends on your skills.

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:48.970
We're from the Anti-Smuggling Brigade.
This is official business.

00:08:48.970 --> 00:08:50.400
Open the door now.

00:08:50.960 --> 00:08:52.370
Our superiors said

00:08:52.630 --> 00:08:55.360
we can't let anyone in
without their permission.

00:08:55.670 --> 00:08:56.280
What's going on?

00:08:56.280 --> 00:08:56.930
Mr. Liu.

00:08:57.150 --> 00:08:58.840
The Anti-Smuggling Brigade is here.

00:08:58.840 --> 00:09:00.300
Anti-Smuggling Brigade?

00:09:00.960 --> 00:09:01.600
Hold on.

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:03.960
Where are they?

00:09:04.030 --> 00:09:05.030
At the front gate.

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:06.730
Keep them busy.

00:09:07.030 --> 00:09:07.790
Got it.

00:09:08.750 --> 00:09:09.950
Move everything out.

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:11.000
Hurry up!

00:09:11.970 --> 00:09:12.900
Hurry up!

00:09:13.480 --> 00:09:15.910
You're obstructing
official duties, you know that?

00:09:15.910 --> 00:09:17.120
Please don't make things difficult for us.

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:18.920
It's not easy for us to find jobs.

00:09:19.080 --> 00:09:20.550
This is your final warning.

00:09:20.550 --> 00:09:23.000
You're suspected
of obstructing official duties.

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:24.360
If you continue to block us,

00:09:24.360 --> 00:09:25.550
we'll take you into custody immediately.

00:09:25.550 --> 00:09:26.870
Sir! Sir!

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:27.990
Please don't upset me.

00:09:27.990 --> 00:09:29.390
I have a heart condition.

00:09:29.630 --> 00:09:31.690
I need to call my supervisor.

00:09:31.790 --> 00:09:32.470
No hurry.

00:09:32.470 --> 00:09:33.720
-Open the door.
-Wait till I make a call.

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.320
You're obstructing
official duties, you know that?

00:09:35.320 --> 00:09:36.580
Come on, open the door.

00:09:36.790 --> 00:09:37.390
Officer.

00:09:37.480 --> 00:09:38.000
Open it!

00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:38.720
You can't come in.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:39.870
You really can't enter.

00:09:39.870 --> 00:09:41.400
I'll be in trouble if you do.

00:09:41.790 --> 00:09:42.750
Stop the act.

00:09:44.790 --> 00:09:45.320
Hurry up!

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:55.720
Mr. Liu,

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:56.790
we can't hold them off anymore.

00:09:56.790 --> 00:09:57.850
They're coming in.

00:09:58.550 --> 00:10:00.630
Find a way to stall them! Find a way!

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:05.480
Stop moving things.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:06.140
Stop it now.

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:07.200
Get the gasoline.

00:10:07.390 --> 00:10:08.520
Bring the fuel cans.

00:10:57.640 --> 00:11:00.480
How did the Anti-Smuggling Bureau
find this place?

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:02.880
I don't know.
They just showed up suddenly.

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:09.290
Uncle Limin.

00:11:13.150 --> 00:11:14.410
I'm fine. Don't worry.

00:11:16.040 --> 00:11:17.300
I burned all the money.

00:11:17.600 --> 00:11:18.600
Left no evidence.

00:11:20.470 --> 00:11:22.000
Who else could it be?

00:11:23.110 --> 00:11:24.750
It must be He who did this.

00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:29.990
Okay. I see.

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:35.030
Mr. Liu, what should we do?

00:11:35.030 --> 00:11:37.160
Get everyone ready. Grab the weapons.

00:11:37.670 --> 00:11:38.800
Let's take him down!

00:12:10.390 --> 00:12:13.590
I heard you're the biggest
human trafficker around here.

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:17.440
You really dare to mess with anyone.

00:12:18.260 --> 00:12:19.050
Mr. Biao.

00:12:20.120 --> 00:12:22.380
I really didn't know he was your brother.

00:12:23.950 --> 00:12:24.750
If I had known,

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:27.390
I definitely wouldn't have taken this job.

00:12:27.390 --> 00:12:27.920
It was...

00:12:28.080 --> 00:12:28.880
A few days ago,

00:12:29.910 --> 00:12:31.110
Liu Tianye came to me.

00:12:31.440 --> 00:12:32.200
He told me to keep an eye

00:12:32.200 --> 00:12:33.150
on the boat where Gang

00:12:33.150 --> 00:12:34.010
was being held.

00:12:35.030 --> 00:12:35.630
Mr. Biao.

00:12:42.130 --> 00:12:42.660
Mr. Biao.

00:12:43.390 --> 00:12:44.990
I really didn't do anything.

00:12:46.480 --> 00:12:47.060
Mr. Biao.

00:13:04.670 --> 00:13:05.360
Tianye,

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:07.510
something happened at the warehouse.

00:13:07.510 --> 00:13:08.710
The money was burned.

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:10.630
Tianfei was taken by He Biao's men.

00:13:10.630 --> 00:13:11.560
Keep an eye on it.

00:13:11.870 --> 00:13:12.500
Tianye,

00:13:12.670 --> 00:13:14.270
there's a call from the dock.

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:16.030
They say He Biao
is looking for the boat everywhere.

00:13:16.030 --> 00:13:16.670
I think

00:13:16.910 --> 00:13:18.240
something's not right.

00:13:18.270 --> 00:13:20.470
How did they know He Gang was on the boat?

00:13:23.280 --> 00:13:25.410
This should be the final round, right?

00:13:26.260 --> 00:13:27.640
When will He Biao arrive?

00:13:27.640 --> 00:13:28.700
He'll be here soon.

00:13:29.550 --> 00:13:30.550
You two get ready.

00:13:31.360 --> 00:13:32.290
Do as I say later.

00:13:32.990 --> 00:13:33.700
Okay.

00:13:42.870 --> 00:13:44.150
He Biao,

00:13:44.800 --> 00:13:46.400
get your ass out here!

00:13:46.950 --> 00:13:48.310
I know you're in there.

00:13:51.770 --> 00:13:52.970
You coward.

00:13:53.030 --> 00:13:54.750
Get out here now!

00:13:59.240 --> 00:14:00.120
You're always

00:14:00.790 --> 00:14:01.910
pretending to be cultured.

00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:04.310
Do you really think you're fooling anyone?

00:14:06.840 --> 00:14:07.720
I know

00:14:08.700 --> 00:14:11.830
you were the one
who reported the warehouse, didn't you?

00:14:15.080 --> 00:14:16.150
It doesn't matter.

00:14:16.750 --> 00:14:18.360
It's just money.

00:14:18.910 --> 00:14:20.480
I don't care.

00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:23.720
I burned everything down.

00:14:24.130 --> 00:14:26.030
The police won't find anything on me.

00:14:26.030 --> 00:14:26.840
Don't worry.

00:14:29.600 --> 00:14:30.440
But let me tell you.

00:14:30.440 --> 00:14:31.150
Shut him up!

00:14:31.150 --> 00:14:32.690
Let me tell you.

00:14:32.870 --> 00:14:33.670
You...

00:14:43.590 --> 00:14:45.830
Don't you think he's a lot like Gang?

00:14:49.870 --> 00:14:52.130
Since he doesn't want to leave the table,

00:14:53.200 --> 00:14:54.610
let him die with the rest.

00:14:58.550 --> 00:14:59.430
Take him away!

00:15:03.120 --> 00:15:03.670
He Biao.

00:15:04.190 --> 00:15:06.150
If you've got the guts, kill me today.

00:15:06.150 --> 00:15:07.630
If you don't kill me,

00:15:08.320 --> 00:15:09.250
sooner or later,

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:11.790
I'll kill you!

00:15:12.310 --> 00:15:13.230
He Biao!

00:15:13.840 --> 00:15:16.480
I'll kill you one day, I swear!

00:15:35.040 --> 00:15:36.500
Captain Qin, we found him.

00:15:46.450 --> 00:15:47.300
It is He Gang.

00:15:49.030 --> 00:15:49.510
Yang.

00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:50.150
Here.

00:15:50.150 --> 00:15:52.080
Contact the fishery authorities.

00:15:52.080 --> 00:15:53.150
Immediately locate

00:15:53.150 --> 00:15:54.080
the position of this vessel.

00:15:54.080 --> 00:15:54.610
Yes, sir.

00:16:08.270 --> 00:16:08.930
Who's this?

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:12.840
This guy looks...

00:16:19.160 --> 00:16:19.250
Pause.

00:16:19.250 --> 00:16:19.870
[Camera]

00:16:19.870 --> 00:16:20.580
Zoom in.

00:16:28.480 --> 00:16:29.480
I've sent you a photo.

00:16:29.480 --> 00:16:30.320
Take a look.

00:16:30.320 --> 00:16:31.290
Is this

00:16:31.750 --> 00:16:33.410
the one who killed Su Hongbao?

00:16:35.390 --> 00:16:37.120
It's him. Where is this person?

00:16:37.450 --> 00:16:38.240
It is him, right?

00:16:38.240 --> 00:16:39.240
Alright, I got it.

00:16:41.080 --> 00:16:41.670
Captain Zhong.

00:16:41.670 --> 00:16:42.630
This person should be

00:16:42.630 --> 00:16:43.770
the killer who murdered Su Hongbao.

00:16:43.770 --> 00:16:44.700
Mai has seen him.

00:16:45.360 --> 00:16:45.960
Is he sure?

00:16:45.990 --> 00:16:46.800
Yes, he's sure.

00:16:46.800 --> 00:16:48.840
How about Zeng Xu and I go find him first?

00:16:48.840 --> 00:16:50.040
Go ahead. Be careful.

00:16:51.670 --> 00:16:52.120
Come on.

00:16:52.120 --> 00:16:53.030
Move. Move.

00:16:55.000 --> 00:16:55.860
Captain Zhong.

00:16:55.930 --> 00:16:57.020
The comrade on surveillance reports

00:16:57.020 --> 00:16:58.240
He Biao has left the tearoom.

00:16:58.240 --> 00:16:58.670
Good.

00:16:58.710 --> 00:16:59.630
Once we get He Gang,

00:16:59.630 --> 00:17:00.480
secure He Biao immediately.

00:17:00.480 --> 00:17:01.010
Yes, sir.

00:17:33.510 --> 00:17:34.970
This house is really nice.

00:17:36.310 --> 00:17:37.440
A lot of people think

00:17:39.360 --> 00:17:41.090
that living in a place like this

00:17:41.510 --> 00:17:43.570
means they can call themselves king.

00:17:45.140 --> 00:17:47.070
But they're just ordinary people.

00:17:49.070 --> 00:17:50.330
Just passing through.

00:17:58.030 --> 00:17:59.110
Uncle Tianye is waiting for you inside.

00:17:59.110 --> 00:17:59.750
Please.

00:18:02.930 --> 00:18:03.640
[Hanzhou Association]

00:18:03.640 --> 00:18:04.570
Wait for me here.

00:18:05.110 --> 00:18:06.110
No need to follow.

00:18:19.650 --> 00:18:20.570
Uncle Tianye.

00:18:21.210 --> 00:18:21.340
[Hanzhou Association]

00:18:21.340 --> 00:18:22.200
He has arrived.

00:18:50.310 --> 00:18:51.240
Please sit down.

00:19:07.440 --> 00:19:08.100
Xiaoshuai.

00:19:09.360 --> 00:19:10.290
You sit down too.

00:19:22.470 --> 00:19:24.070
What would you like to drink?

00:19:25.700 --> 00:19:26.690
This sofa

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:27.940
is uncomfortable.

00:19:29.830 --> 00:19:31.030
Because it's my sofa.

00:19:35.830 --> 00:19:36.830
Where is Tianfei?

00:19:38.120 --> 00:19:39.070
Tianye, don't you think

00:19:39.070 --> 00:19:41.000
Tianfei and Gang are very similar?

00:19:41.360 --> 00:19:43.160
They're impulsive and reckless,

00:19:43.160 --> 00:19:44.990
just like spoiled children.

00:19:45.550 --> 00:19:48.080
You should discipline him
when you have time,

00:19:48.590 --> 00:19:50.850
or he'll get into serious trouble later.

00:19:51.370 --> 00:19:53.640
Don't you think you and I
are very similar too?

00:19:53.640 --> 00:19:54.920
You have cards up your sleeve.

00:19:54.920 --> 00:19:56.520
I have cards up my sleeve too.

00:19:56.550 --> 00:19:58.680
You want a seat at the table, and so do I.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:00.720
What are we going to do about that?

00:20:00.720 --> 00:20:02.890
That last hand on the boat—

00:20:04.840 --> 00:20:06.900
neither of us ever saw the hole cards.

00:20:07.900 --> 00:20:09.270
Let's play another round.

00:20:09.270 --> 00:20:10.930
Sure. What do you want to play?

00:20:12.550 --> 00:20:13.380
Mark Six.

00:20:13.550 --> 00:20:14.750
Betting on odd or even.

00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:15.610
All about luck.

00:20:17.110 --> 00:20:18.020
Go get a TV,

00:20:18.440 --> 00:20:19.970
so Mr. He can enjoy himself.

00:20:20.110 --> 00:20:20.680
Okay.

00:20:22.830 --> 00:20:23.400
Mr. He,

00:20:25.160 --> 00:20:26.360
I actually want to see

00:20:26.960 --> 00:20:27.830
between you and me,

00:20:27.830 --> 00:20:29.560
whose fate is actually better.

00:20:29.640 --> 00:20:31.030
You know, the two of us

00:20:31.400 --> 00:20:33.000
were born with the same fate.

00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:36.450
We both hold a bad hand of cards.

00:20:36.880 --> 00:20:38.750
The key is how we play them.

00:20:43.400 --> 00:20:44.920
Today I'll take a step back.

00:20:44.920 --> 00:20:46.720
I'll return your brother to you.

00:20:46.920 --> 00:20:47.480
I'll buy

00:20:48.340 --> 00:20:49.360
your entire business.

00:20:49.360 --> 00:20:50.290
Name your price.

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:52.680
But both of you must leave Hanzhou.

00:20:53.480 --> 00:20:54.750
I'm not forcing you to leave.

00:20:54.750 --> 00:20:56.170
Your brother fired the shots.

00:20:56.170 --> 00:20:57.680
The police are watching you both now.

00:20:57.680 --> 00:20:59.310
If you don't leave, this won't end.

00:20:59.310 --> 00:21:01.570
I've stayed in Hanzhou for so many years.

00:21:05.480 --> 00:21:07.610
A man with dignity can't just run away.

00:21:08.130 --> 00:21:09.990
Then there's nothing to discuss.

00:21:10.200 --> 00:21:11.160
If the two of us fight it out,

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:12.560
we'll both end up losing.

00:21:14.070 --> 00:21:15.670
Others will benefit from it.

00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:18.600
But since things
have escalated to this point,

00:21:18.880 --> 00:21:21.210
we'll have to settle this
once and for all.

00:21:51.460 --> 00:21:52.120
Gang.

00:21:52.240 --> 00:21:52.590
Gang.

00:21:53.110 --> 00:21:53.840
Are you okay?

00:21:55.650 --> 00:21:56.780
Where's my brother?

00:21:57.030 --> 00:21:58.240
He went to Liu Tianye.

00:22:02.440 --> 00:22:03.100
Be careful.

00:22:06.200 --> 00:22:06.680
Gang.

00:22:08.400 --> 00:22:09.350
Can I go now?

00:22:10.070 --> 00:22:12.400
I really didn't know you were Gang before.

00:22:39.860 --> 00:22:40.990
The blood isn't dry.

00:22:41.000 --> 00:22:42.000
They can't be far.

00:22:42.420 --> 00:22:43.440
Notify the whole city to search.

00:22:43.440 --> 00:22:44.000
Yes.

00:22:53.640 --> 00:22:54.260
Captain Zhong,

00:22:54.260 --> 00:22:55.660
we haven't found He Gang.

00:22:55.900 --> 00:22:57.230
Search more carefully.

00:22:57.270 --> 00:22:57.750
Yes.

00:22:57.840 --> 00:22:58.570
Understood.

00:22:59.720 --> 00:23:00.300
Mentor.

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:02.200
An anonymous caller

00:23:02.200 --> 00:23:04.270
reported that He Biao
had detained someone over a debt

00:23:04.270 --> 00:23:06.070
and was holding him at Elegance.

00:23:06.560 --> 00:23:08.160
Send the Second Squad there.

00:23:08.640 --> 00:23:10.240
If they find any trace of He Biao,

00:23:10.240 --> 00:23:11.360
detain him immediately.

00:23:11.360 --> 00:23:11.920
Okay.

00:23:15.920 --> 00:23:17.750
The highly anticipated Mark Six lottery

00:23:17.750 --> 00:23:19.830
draw is now officially beginning.

00:23:20.900 --> 00:23:21.960
The first number is

00:23:22.480 --> 00:23:23.200
seven.

00:23:27.790 --> 00:23:28.960
He is safe now.

00:23:28.960 --> 00:23:30.610
My men have picked up Gang.

00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:32.260
Your leverage is gone.

00:23:34.680 --> 00:23:36.140
Consider it a gift from me.

00:23:38.450 --> 00:23:39.470
Next is

00:23:39.720 --> 00:23:40.580
twenty-three.

00:23:43.440 --> 00:23:44.570
Where did He Biao go?

00:23:44.910 --> 00:23:46.520
To Qiao Defu's villa.

00:23:49.030 --> 00:23:50.110
Call Captain Zhong right away

00:23:50.110 --> 00:23:50.640
and report this.

00:23:50.640 --> 00:23:51.200
Yes.

00:23:51.480 --> 00:23:52.200
Captain!

00:23:54.110 --> 00:23:54.640
Captain.

00:23:54.920 --> 00:23:56.440
We found a hidden room over there.

00:23:56.440 --> 00:23:56.970
Let's go.

00:24:02.200 --> 00:24:02.640
Okay.

00:24:03.160 --> 00:24:03.490
Okay.

00:24:05.210 --> 00:24:05.810
Copy that.

00:24:07.560 --> 00:24:08.020
Liu.

00:24:08.910 --> 00:24:10.970
He Biao went to Qiao Defu's holiday villa.

00:24:10.970 --> 00:24:11.500
Let's go.

00:24:11.680 --> 00:24:12.030
Yes.

00:24:23.850 --> 00:24:24.500
Zeng Xu,

00:24:24.830 --> 00:24:26.510
based on the information you provided,

00:24:26.510 --> 00:24:28.550
we've located where this truck
was parked before.

00:24:28.550 --> 00:24:30.920
It's at the truck logistics center
in the west of the city.

00:24:30.920 --> 00:24:31.510
Got it.

00:24:31.510 --> 00:24:33.110
We'll head there right away.

00:24:33.790 --> 00:24:36.720
At the truck logistics center
in the west of the city.

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:39.680
Eighteen.

00:24:40.160 --> 00:24:41.590
Finally got an even number.

00:24:41.590 --> 00:24:44.050
You don't have to go
bare-bottomed anymore.

00:24:47.270 --> 00:24:48.870
The police rescued Tianfei.

00:24:50.030 --> 00:24:51.630
The police rescued Tianfei.

00:24:52.400 --> 00:24:54.400
Elegance must be full of police now.

00:24:54.790 --> 00:24:55.590
Your leverage

00:24:55.850 --> 00:24:57.050
is gone too, isn't it?

00:24:57.240 --> 00:24:58.500
As long as Gang is safe,

00:24:59.530 --> 00:25:01.190
I have nothing to worry about.

00:25:02.190 --> 00:25:04.120
He Gang's life means nothing to me.

00:25:04.480 --> 00:25:05.940
I know you found that boat.

00:25:06.350 --> 00:25:08.030
I deliberately let you find it.

00:25:08.030 --> 00:25:08.890
I'm interested

00:25:09.030 --> 00:25:11.210
in your protector
at the Public Security Bureau.

00:25:11.210 --> 00:25:11.810
I want him.

00:25:12.690 --> 00:25:13.690
You can't get him.

00:25:15.270 --> 00:25:16.420
He looks down on you.

00:25:33.030 --> 00:25:37.830
[Yongsheng Tail Lift]

00:25:40.550 --> 00:25:41.750
We're with
the Hanzhou Public Security Bureau.

00:25:41.750 --> 00:25:42.960
Have you seen this person

00:25:42.960 --> 00:25:43.960
and this vehicle?

00:25:45.960 --> 00:25:47.030
Isn't this Guazi?

00:25:47.640 --> 00:25:48.610
What did he do?

00:25:48.750 --> 00:25:49.950
You know this person?

00:25:50.680 --> 00:25:52.810
Sometimes he stays here for a few days.

00:25:53.030 --> 00:25:54.160
This guy is strange.

00:25:54.590 --> 00:25:56.510
No one knows what cargo he transports.

00:25:56.510 --> 00:25:57.640
He lives in his truck

00:25:57.830 --> 00:25:58.590
and loves snacking on sunflower seeds.

00:25:58.590 --> 00:25:59.240
So we

00:25:59.240 --> 00:26:00.570
gave him that nickname.

00:26:01.040 --> 00:26:03.240
But we don't have much contact with him.

00:26:04.310 --> 00:26:05.170
Where is he now?

00:26:07.110 --> 00:26:08.040
He was just here.

00:26:08.200 --> 00:26:08.860
Where is he?

00:26:09.480 --> 00:26:10.750
He seems to have left already.

00:26:10.750 --> 00:26:12.210
He's been gone for a while.

00:26:12.400 --> 00:26:13.330
Okay, thank you.

00:26:36.720 --> 00:26:38.050
It's your new identity.

00:26:38.510 --> 00:26:40.240
Your route have been arranged.

00:26:40.530 --> 00:26:41.860
After leaving Hanzhou,

00:26:42.440 --> 00:26:44.040
contact that person inside.

00:26:44.090 --> 00:26:45.630
He'll help you get out.

00:26:47.920 --> 00:26:48.510
Sir,

00:26:50.010 --> 00:26:51.360
after I leave,

00:26:52.240 --> 00:26:53.970
please take care of my brother.

00:26:54.680 --> 00:26:55.810
I'm counting on you.

00:27:06.850 --> 00:27:08.250
Three odds, three evens.

00:27:08.330 --> 00:27:10.260
Looks like luck is still on my side.

00:27:39.710 --> 00:27:42.770
[Incoming call]

00:27:43.670 --> 00:27:44.400
Speak.

00:27:46.640 --> 00:27:47.310
Sir.

00:27:48.550 --> 00:27:49.280
Don't worry.

00:27:49.510 --> 00:27:51.110
Those photos won't get out.

00:27:51.610 --> 00:27:52.160
[Work call]

00:27:52.160 --> 00:27:54.260
I'd like to be friends with you.

00:27:55.030 --> 00:27:57.030
I heard you and Mr. He go way back.

00:27:58.310 --> 00:27:58.920
Why don't you

00:27:58.920 --> 00:28:00.160
talk to him for me?

00:28:03.590 --> 00:28:04.510
Don't think

00:28:04.510 --> 00:28:06.640
a few photos like these mean anything.

00:28:07.640 --> 00:28:09.070
Everything about Longwan

00:28:09.070 --> 00:28:10.400
is already on our radar.

00:28:11.310 --> 00:28:13.310
Your good little brother, Qin Feng,

00:28:13.550 --> 00:28:14.830
has his eyes on you.

00:28:16.880 --> 00:28:17.680
Just like you,

00:28:17.830 --> 00:28:18.830
trying to climb higher—

00:28:18.830 --> 00:28:20.490
there's always a price to pay.

00:28:20.860 --> 00:28:21.210
[Work call]

00:28:21.210 --> 00:28:22.030
Biao.

00:28:22.340 --> 00:28:23.090
Yes, sir.

00:28:24.200 --> 00:28:26.060
You shouldn't have gone this far.

00:28:26.840 --> 00:28:29.000
I promised to make introductions for you.

00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:29.850
I did that.

00:28:32.720 --> 00:28:34.680
I wish you success in your career.

00:28:36.000 --> 00:28:37.960
Your brother has already left.

00:28:39.510 --> 00:28:40.370
Let me tell you.

00:28:40.550 --> 00:28:42.350
The police are watching you now.

00:28:42.350 --> 00:28:44.010
Don't cause any more trouble.

00:28:44.070 --> 00:28:45.530
If anything else happens,

00:28:45.590 --> 00:28:47.250
no one will be able to help you.

00:28:47.820 --> 00:28:48.710
My advice is

00:28:49.350 --> 00:28:50.080
you'd better

00:28:50.410 --> 00:28:51.380
leave Hanzhou.

00:28:52.110 --> 00:28:53.510
That's your best option.

00:28:56.110 --> 00:28:57.000
Next,

00:28:57.000 --> 00:28:59.240
we'll draw the final special number.

00:29:06.770 --> 00:29:08.230
The special number is out.

00:29:11.200 --> 00:29:12.160
Twenty-eight.

00:29:14.600 --> 00:29:16.260
Three singles, four doubles.

00:29:16.480 --> 00:29:17.160
I won.

00:29:17.220 --> 00:29:18.140
Is this fate?

00:29:27.640 --> 00:29:28.900
I've never understood

00:29:30.310 --> 00:29:31.720
what exactly you want.

00:29:32.630 --> 00:29:33.270
To win.

00:29:43.720 --> 00:29:44.640
I hope

00:29:46.390 --> 00:29:47.720
you can win till the end.

00:30:01.860 --> 00:30:02.460
Mr. He.

00:30:05.590 --> 00:30:06.590
When we were on the boat,

00:30:06.590 --> 00:30:08.790
you said you'd decide who wins or loses.

00:30:08.920 --> 00:30:10.080
But here,

00:30:10.400 --> 00:30:12.110
heaven decides the outcome.

00:30:39.980 --> 00:30:40.720
Liu Tianye.

00:30:42.040 --> 00:30:44.240
Chances are that heaven's on your side,

00:30:44.540 --> 00:30:47.140
but whether you get to see
this card tonight...

00:30:49.560 --> 00:30:50.490
is up to me.

00:30:55.110 --> 00:30:55.590
Mr. He,

00:30:55.680 --> 00:30:56.480
see you later.

00:31:19.350 --> 00:31:20.460
I have three Aces.

00:31:20.880 --> 00:31:22.410
How are you going to beat me?

00:31:23.170 --> 00:31:24.550
What if I got a straight?

00:31:56.960 --> 00:31:58.030
Brother!

00:31:58.480 --> 00:32:00.220
You must take care of yourself!

00:34:03.350 --> 00:34:04.000
Drive!

00:34:04.480 --> 00:34:05.110
Drive!

00:34:11.980 --> 00:34:12.420
What?

00:34:14.840 --> 00:34:15.639
Car accident?

00:34:15.920 --> 00:34:16.620
Got it.

00:34:20.030 --> 00:34:22.400
Traffic police said they found
that a 4.2-meter box truck

00:34:22.400 --> 00:34:24.280
hit an unlicensed vehicle near Binhai Road

00:34:24.280 --> 00:34:26.510
and took away the driver
of the unlicensed vehicle.

00:34:26.510 --> 00:34:27.190
They checked the surveillance footage

00:34:27.190 --> 00:34:28.480
and said this a 4.2-meter box truck

00:34:28.480 --> 00:34:31.139
went to a small village
in the northwest corner.

00:35:23.280 --> 00:35:24.880
The police have found you.

00:35:24.920 --> 00:35:26.080
Clean it up.

00:37:03.730 --> 00:37:04.590
Captain Zhong.

00:37:06.880 --> 00:37:08.070
We've found He Gang.

00:38:33.710 --> 00:38:35.110
To Hanzhou Association.

00:38:36.440 --> 00:38:37.030
He Biao.

00:38:38.000 --> 00:38:39.190
You've already lost.

00:38:39.190 --> 00:38:40.280
It's useless to find Uncle Tianye.

00:38:40.280 --> 00:38:41.150
You can't kill him.

00:38:41.150 --> 00:38:43.550
Whether I can kill him
or not is my business!

00:38:44.630 --> 00:38:45.490
Let me tell you.

00:38:47.190 --> 00:38:48.790
Everyone has their own fate.

00:38:49.360 --> 00:38:50.280
Gang was beaten by you.

00:38:50.280 --> 00:38:51.420
That was his fate.

00:38:51.670 --> 00:38:54.070
Today you fall by my hand.
That's your fate!

00:38:56.400 --> 00:38:57.930
Let's not blame each other.

00:38:58.920 --> 00:39:00.520
I've never believed in fate.

00:39:00.960 --> 00:39:02.880
I believe hard work
will always be rewarded.

00:39:02.880 --> 00:39:04.430
The day we were born,

00:39:04.880 --> 00:39:06.940
everything was already determined.

00:39:07.110 --> 00:39:07.710
Faster!

00:39:09.910 --> 00:39:12.080
Do you know
what the fairest thing in the world is?

00:39:12.080 --> 00:39:12.880
[May Wealth Flow In]

00:39:12.880 --> 00:39:15.700
Bullets make everyone bleed.

00:39:15.880 --> 00:39:16.880
Everyone bleeds.

00:39:17.670 --> 00:39:18.730
Don't fear others.

00:39:18.800 --> 00:39:21.060
You're no worse than anyone else, right?

00:39:21.320 --> 00:39:22.520
You're from Longwan.

00:39:22.840 --> 00:39:23.360
Our fate

00:39:24.190 --> 00:39:25.050
can be changed.

00:39:26.030 --> 00:39:26.900
He Biao.

00:39:28.110 --> 00:39:30.480
It doesn't matter
if you believe in fate or not.

00:39:30.480 --> 00:39:33.610
But I believe there's one thing
that's absolutely fair.

00:39:33.800 --> 00:39:35.800
Whether you're a boss or underling,

00:39:36.190 --> 00:39:37.790
whether you're rich or poor,

00:39:39.440 --> 00:39:40.700
you only have one life!

00:40:17.240 --> 00:40:19.570
Why did He Biao
come looking for you today?

00:40:19.960 --> 00:40:21.760
We had some business dispute.

00:40:22.430 --> 00:40:23.760
He thinks I stole his business,

00:40:23.760 --> 00:40:25.490
so he came to threaten us today.

00:40:27.710 --> 00:40:29.310
If it weren't for Xiaoshuai,

00:40:29.630 --> 00:40:31.960
I might have been
the one in trouble today.

00:40:34.320 --> 00:40:35.320
Get him in the car.

00:40:35.630 --> 00:40:36.760
Take him back to the bureau
for a statement.

00:40:36.760 --> 00:40:37.280
Got it.

00:41:00.480 --> 00:41:01.340
Captain Zhong.

00:41:02.210 --> 00:41:03.140
What happened?

00:41:03.510 --> 00:41:04.600
Ding Xiaoshuai

00:41:05.440 --> 00:41:07.570
got into a car accident with He Biao.

00:41:08.670 --> 00:41:09.930
By the time we arrived,

00:41:10.840 --> 00:41:12.440
Ding Xiaoshuai already had no pulse.

00:41:12.440 --> 00:41:14.100
He is still in emergency care.

00:41:15.950 --> 00:41:17.210
What about Liu Tianye?

00:41:17.440 --> 00:41:19.110
We're taking him back to
the bureau to get a statement.

00:41:19.110 --> 00:41:20.170
He Biao is dead too?

00:41:28.850 --> 00:41:30.780
Let's get back to the bureau first.

00:41:31.840 --> 00:41:35.420
[Hanzhou Central Hospital]

00:41:42.030 --> 00:41:43.490
Xiaoshuai, you're awake.

00:41:43.710 --> 00:41:44.840
How are you feeling?

00:41:59.190 --> 00:42:00.250
What about He Biao?

00:42:01.360 --> 00:42:01.960
Is he dead?

00:42:10.190 --> 00:42:11.120
Ding Xiaoshuai.

00:42:12.100 --> 00:42:13.960
We need to ask you a few questions.

00:42:15.550 --> 00:42:16.150
Wen Bo,

00:42:17.550 --> 00:42:18.480
give us a moment.

00:42:31.360 --> 00:42:32.070
Tell me

00:42:32.710 --> 00:42:33.770
what happened yesterday.

00:42:33.770 --> 00:42:39.120
[Ward 5]

00:42:49.590 --> 00:42:50.550
He Biao is dead.

00:42:51.150 --> 00:42:53.010
He Gang has been taken care of too.

00:42:54.400 --> 00:42:55.230
I think

00:42:55.760 --> 00:42:57.760
since the Longwan people
want a seat at the table,

00:42:57.760 --> 00:42:58.690
we can keep them.

00:42:59.590 --> 00:43:00.760
But we need

00:43:01.440 --> 00:43:02.670
our own people with them.